#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:1
msgid "Configuring shortcuts in Krita."
msgstr "在 Krita 中自訂快捷鍵。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:16
msgid "Shortcut Settings"
msgstr "「鍵盤快捷鍵」設定"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:18
msgid ""
"Configuring shortcuts is another way to customize the application to fit "
"you.  Whether you are transitioning from another app, like Photoshop or "
"MyPaint, or you think your own shortcut keys make more sense for you then "
"Krita has got you covered.  You get to the shortcuts interface through :"
"menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Krita...` and by choosing the :"
"menuselection:`Keyboard Shortcuts` tab."
msgstr ""
"一套適當的快捷鍵設置可以提高工作效率。您可以自訂 Krita 快捷以符合本身使用習"
"慣，若您由 PhotoShop 或 MyPaint 軟體轉移過來，或覺得自訂的快捷鍵在作業上更有"
"幫助，那麼 Krita 自訂快捷鍵功能可以滿足您的需求。您可在\\ :menuselection:"
"`「設定 」--> 「設定 Krita…」`\\ 打開設定視窗進入\\ :menuselection:`「鍵盤快"
"捷鍵」`\\ 分頁裡面開始配置您的快捷鍵。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:20
msgid ""
"Most of Krita's shortcuts are configured in the menu section :menuselection:"
"`Settings --> Configure Krita... --> Shortcuts`. The shortcuts configured "
"here are simple key combinations, for example the :kbd:`Ctrl + X` shortcut "
"to cut. Shortcuts can also be sequences of key combinations (e.g. :kbd:"
"`Shift + S` shortcut then the :kbd:`B` key). Krita also has a special "
"interface for configuring the mouse and stylus events sent to the canvas, "
"found under :ref:`canvas_input_settings`."
msgstr ""
"Krita 大部分快捷鍵都可以在\\ :menuselection:`「設定」--> 「Krita 設定...」 --"
"> 「鍵盤快捷鍵」`\\ 頁面中進行設定。此處設定都是簡單的組合鍵，例如 Ctrl+X 快"
"捷鍵可以用以剪切。某些快捷鍵可以按順序組合，例如按 Shift+S 可以叫出吸附選單，"
"然後按 TAB 鍵來選取吸附選項（譯者註：原文中 B 按鍵於此處似乎無效，B 鍵現為手"
"繪筆刷工具的熱鍵）。Krita 還有一個特殊介面用來設定發送到畫布的滑鼠與觸控筆事"
"件，可以在\\ :ref:`canvas_input_settings`\\ 中找到。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:22
msgid ""
"To use, just type the :guilabel:`Action` into the Search box you want to "
"assign/reassign the shortcut for.  Suppose we wanted to assign the shortcut :"
"kbd:`Ctrl + G` to the :guilabel:`Action` of Group Layers so that every time "
"we pressed the :kbd:`Ctrl + G` shortcut a new Layer Group would be created.  "
"Use the following steps to do this:"
msgstr ""
"設定方法：只需在「搜尋」欄位中輸入\\ :guilabel:`操作`\\ ，然後給它指定快捷"
"鍵。假設您想把 :kbd:`Ctrl + G` 指定給圖層的操作，以便於每次按下 :kbd:`Ctrl + "
"G` 後，自動建立一個新圖層群組，請依照以下步驟："

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:24
msgid "Type \"Group Layer\"."
msgstr "輸入\"快速建立群組\"。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:25
msgid "Click on Group Layer and a small inset box will open."
msgstr "以滑鼠點一下「快速建立群組」，這時會打開一個小對話盒。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:26
msgid "Click the Custom radio button."
msgstr "點一下「自訂」單選按鈕。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:27
msgid "Click on the first button and type the :kbd:`Ctrl + G` shortcut."
msgstr ""
"接著點一下旁邊的「無」之後會變成「輸入」，請在這裡按下\\ :kbd:`Ctrl + G`\\ 組"
"合鍵。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:28
msgid "Click OK."
msgstr "單擊右下方的「確定」即可。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:30
msgid ""
"From this point on, whenever you press the :kbd:`Ctrl + G` shortcut you'll "
"get a new :guilabel:`Group Layer`."
msgstr ""
"從現在開始，當您按下 :kbd:`Ctrl + G` 之後，都會自動建立一個新\\ :guilabel:`圖"
"層群組`\\ 。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:33
msgid ""
"Smart use of shortcuts can save you significant time and further streamline "
"your workflow."
msgstr "靈活使用快捷鍵可以為您節省大量時間，並進一步簡化您的工作流程。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:37
msgid ""
"Actions, which includes everything that can be assigned a shortcut, can now "
"be searched with :kbd:`Ctrl + Enter`, reducing the need to assign a shortcut "
"to every single action. This itself is called the :guilabel:`Search Actions` "
"shortcut, and can also be reassigned if desired."
msgstr ""
"您可以隨時按下 :kbd:`Ctrl + Enter` 組合鍵開啟\\ :guilabel:`搜尋操作`\\ 輸入以"
"搜尋所有可用的功能，從而減少不必要的快捷鍵分配。您也可以為這個功能另外指定快"
"捷鍵。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:40
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "選單項目"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:42
msgid "Search bar"
msgstr "搜尋欄位"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:43
msgid ""
"Entering text here will search for matching shortcuts in the shortcut list."
msgstr "在這裡輸入文字可以在列表中搜尋符合輸入字串的快捷鍵。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:44
msgid "Shortcut List"
msgstr "快捷鍵列表"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:45
msgid ""
"Shortcuts are organized into sections. Each shortcut can be given a primary "
"and alternate key combination."
msgstr ""
"快捷鍵在列表中依照屬性分組，每一個操作都可以有一個主快捷鍵和備選快捷鍵。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:47
msgid "Load/Save Shortcuts Profiles"
msgstr "載入/儲存快捷鍵設定檔"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:47
msgid ""
"The bottom row of buttons contains commands for exporting and import "
"keyboard shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"此設定頁面底部有一排按鈕，可用於建立、刪除、儲存、載入和列印目前快捷鍵方案。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:52
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "設定"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:55
msgid "Primary and alternate shortcuts"
msgstr "主要和備選快捷鍵"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:55
msgid ""
"Each shortcut is assigned a default, which may be empty. The user can assign "
"up to two custom shortcuts, known as primary and alternate shortcuts. Simply "
"click on a \"Custom\" button and type the key combination you wish to assign "
"to the shortcut. If the key combination is already in use for another "
"shortcut, the dialog will prompt the user to resolve the conflict."
msgstr ""
"每個操作項目都分配了一個預設值，但可能是空的設定。使用者最多可以指派兩個自定"
"快捷鍵，稱為「主要快捷鍵」和「備選快捷鍵」。只需要單擊\"自訂\"按鈕並按下您想"
"指派給操作項目的快捷鍵組合。若按下的組合鍵已被別的操作佔用，將會提示您目前快"
"捷鍵有衝突 ，讓您選擇要如何處理。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:58
msgid "Shortcut schemes"
msgstr "快捷鍵方案"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:58
msgid ""
"Many users migrate to Krita from other tools with different default "
"shortcuts. Krita users may change the default shortcuts to mimic these other "
"programs.  Currently, Krita ships with defaults for Photoshop and Paint Tool "
"Sai. Additional shortcut schemes can be placed in the ~/.config/krita/input/ "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"您可以從快捷鍵方案選單中隨時切換不同快捷鍵方案。Krita 附帶了 PhotoShop和 "
"Paint Tool Sai 的預設快捷鍵設定。您可以將額外的快捷鍵方案保存在 ~/.config/"
"krita/input/ 資料夾中。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:62
msgid "Saving, loading and sharing custom shortcuts"
msgstr "儲存、載入和分享自訂快捷鍵"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/shortcut_settings.rst:61
msgid ""
"Users may wish to export their shortcuts to use across machines, or even "
"share with other users. This can be done with the save/load drop-down. Note: "
"the shortcuts can be saved and overridden manually by backingup the text "
"file kritashortcutsrc located in ~/.config/krita/.  Additionally, the user "
"can export a custom shortcut scheme file generated by merging the existing "
"scheme defaults with the current customizations."
msgstr ""
"您可能希望將快捷鍵的設定沿用在不同電腦、不同平台或與別的使用者共享設定。這可"
"以按下「儲存」/「載入」下拉選單來完成。您也可以在 ~/.config/krita/ 資料夾中"
"將 kritashortcutsrc 手動複製來備份或覆蓋新的快捷鍵方案。此外也可以導出現有方"
"案預設值與當前自訂項目合併以產生新的自訂快捷鍵方案。"

